trans-unit.source: Supports a simple iteration over a <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 支持简单遍历<xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Collection"></xref>对象。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators provide read-only access to the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器提供对集合中的数据的只读访问。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器不能用于修改基础集合。

trans-unit.source: Initially, the enumerator is positioned before the first element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 最初，枚举数定位在集合中的第一个元素之前。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Reset%2A> method also brings the enumerator back to this position.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Reset%2A>方法还会枚举器放回此位置。</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Reset%2A>

trans-unit.source: At this position, calling the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A> property throws an exception.
trans-unit.target: 在此位置，调用<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>属性引发异常。</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: Therefore, you must call the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.MoveNext%2A> method to advance the enumerator to the first element of the collection before reading the value of <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 因此，必须调用该<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>方法的第一个元素的集合，然后再读取<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.Current%2A>的值枚举器向前</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2Enumerator.MoveNext%2A>
